{"tid":958510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖曼聯回歸？】紅魔終極兵器將復出","createTime":"2018-12-28T01:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T02:48:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aaaa0541112febd825173932fc795c41f60029c8","tid":958510,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:07:11.000Z","msg":"　曼聯3-1輕取哈特斯菲爾德，蘇斯克查賽後點名盛讚了普巴。索帥還表示自己上任一週以來主要是幫助球員調整心態，真正戰術層面的東西需要時間才能做出改變。<br />\n<br />\n　　蘇斯克查談普巴：「這才是我認識的保羅，他在預備隊時我就認識他了。他一直是一個開心的男孩，臉上總掛著大大的微笑。當你為曼聯效力，你應該開心。當然這也是一種責任，但是為曼聯效力也是一種榮譽和特權，他一直是一個曼聯的孩子。他知道為曼聯效力的意義。保羅上一場創造了兩三次機會，這場攻入了兩個入球，我希望他能享受這些。」<br />\n<br />\n　　蘇斯克查談比賽：「當我們攻入第二個入球，你可以看出來信心的增強和前進的態度。但是我們需要學著放慢比賽的節奏，在對手的半場踢球。我們在這點上做得不夠好。在短短一週時間內，除了心態，你改變不了任何事情。我想要我的球隊按特定的方式踢球，要給他們一些指示，這是一個正在進行的過程。球員需要時間才能瞭解教練要求的細節，我想我已經做了一些微小的調整。」<br />\n<br />\n　　蘇斯克查還確認山齊士即將復出，他說：「山齊士已經回來了了，上週五飛回來的。他已經進行了兩天的康復訓練，希望他能盡快加入有球訓練。對陣般尼茅夫比賽復出很懸，但對陣紐卡他肯定能參加。我還沒和他坐下來詳談過，聖誕期間我們放了假，他仍在堅持訓練，看起來他就像個工作狂。」"},{"pid":"0c9a91178519829dbe875a06bc78fe3b2b0f211a","tid":958510,"uid":5549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"山神回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8e2d79aff2c86c9a74e74304c56e24b259f5cc","tid":958510,"uid":129835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d89cb7360aa2972c8902d4e05706cc6d51744a","tid":958510,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"仲有無"},{"pid":"847467ccf4fbd179cc98057f4d39e6c7fdbfa8b3","tid":958510,"uid":102603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:13:45.000Z","msg":"後追開始猁今年都係無緣"},{"pid":"c1270404b38799aea1c5c79fbf0c994cf9e39603","tid":958510,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔知搵唔搵到山神使用說明書呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acec74b38a5554626157876ed024fd0307b6a54","tid":958510,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"神魔終極合一<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6db8f8e6d1fb46034abec95ddcb8fb63a2df35f","tid":958510,"uid":16343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾復出之後咪又係一舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e90ecdb4e1a230fe72c897c046575ce3a6fdf4","tid":958510,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1270404b38799aea1c5c79fbf0c994cf9e39603","tid":958510,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔知搵唔搵到山神使用說明書呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"爺爺用用下唔見咗，可能俾蘇B汁到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4123e0f45afd6cbe63dc0835f6a6fcb0a7dff6f5","tid":958510,"uid":37325,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"仲以為4424<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係神魔合一<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271a7c05b1332f7b344618bbacba09cdf619606f","tid":958510,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 球賽終結者山神"},{"pid":"f0cb6738b21ac31b7531da4bfb73841c7bb087eb","tid":958510,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"